Dirvish Web Interface
=====================

See AUTHORS and COPYRIGHT for the list of contributors.

Install
=======

* Install Dirvish, see howto :
		en -> http://www.dirvish.org/debian.howto.html
		fr -> http://blog.pablo-ruth.fr/index.php/dirvish-sauvegarde-automatique-et-incrementale-via-ssh/

* Install a webserver with php5 support
  - Exemple with apache : apt-get install apache2 php5
* Clone all files in your webserver root folder 
  - With apache : git clone git://github.com/pablor44/dirvish-web-interface.git /var/www/dirvish-web-interface
* Copy exemple config file to create your config file
  - cd /var/www/dirvish-web-interface && cp config.php.exemple config.php
* Edit config file and replace path to master dirvish config file if necessary

* Now you can access web interface in your browser : http://localhost/dirvish-web-interface/
